data.description: Welcome to 88 Brookfield! A quaint yet spacious 2 bedroom, 1.5 bath colonial converted from 3 bedroom for a larger primary. Built in 1929 and renovated within the past 10 years. The entry foyer has been repurposed into a home office space but can be utilized as a 3rd bedroom. This is a turn key home offering spacious rooms and an enormous 400x100 park-like yard with specimen trees. There is a large 2 car detached garage and full basement used as a workshop with bilco doors for easy access. Located close to town for shopping and easy access to the highway. Won't Last!
